---
title: Halloumi Tray Bake with Mediterranean Roasted Vegetables and Pesto Drizzle
description: For a real taste of the Mediterranean, this dish has it all. Potatoes, courgettes, peppers and onions are roasted together before the halloumi is added for the final 20 minutes until everything is deliciously golden. Serve up, finish off the flavours with a pesto drizzle and dive in! Minimal washing up, quick to prep, and packed with fresh summery flavours, this recipe is perfect for feeding a crowd.
